data.description: Welcome home to this sprawling end unit in the gated Creekwood subdivision of Algonquin.  This former model home has plenty of natural light and features vaulted ceilings in the main living areas, hardwood floors, and a first floor master bedroom with its own ensuite.  The main floor office has floor to ceiling built ins and beautiful french doors - a work from home dream.  The kitchen's tall cabinets, stainless steel appliances, vent hood, center island and granite counters are a chef's delight.  The second and third bedrooms can be found up the stairs. The fourth bedroom is located in the spacious walkout basement with it's own living area, full bath and walk in closet.  Plenty of storage throughout.  The back deck is perfect for entertaining guests.  Updates include New HWH 2023, professionally painted, kitchen cabinets refaced, new basement flooring and trim. Close to shopping, dining, entertainment and expressway. Sold As Is.  Schedule your tour today!
